  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">\"A spirit bird whose cry heralds the dawn; a morning star that lights the dark night.\"</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">The \"Nightveil Piercer\" Motorbike Premium Model will go live after the Version 3.5 update. Take a look at its details.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"3\" data-line=\"true\">✦How to Obtain✦</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"4\" data-line=\"true\">After the Version 3.5 update, the \"Nightveil Piercer\" Premium Model Set Bundle will be permanently available in the Vehicle Looks Store. The Bundle includes \"Nightveil Piercer\" Premium Model x1 and Astrite x600, priced at 29.99 USD.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"4\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/zl2evqvnkhz0n7eqcv-1782888580279.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/pgycua797vu8frmzc2-1782888596747.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/rx011oxfnlxdra90cl-1782888614984.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1782835200000/u90mu4yt9wbef2wizn-1782888631344.gif\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"4\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
